pcp - The Producer of C++ Programs
Version 1.1
Copyright (C) 2011 Nabil Hassein, Thomas Huston, Mike Morreale, Marta Wilgan

Supported ant commands:

ant            : defaults to src
ant src        : compiles the source code
ant jar        : builds a jar file
ant translate  : translates a file specified by the flag -Dfile=/path/to/file
ant ast        : outputs the ast for a file specified by the flag -Dfile=/path/to/file
ant docs       : generates javadocs
ant clean      : deletes the classes and dist directories
